issueGroups.name: Proj - Tasks
issueGroups.query: project != LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND (((assignee was 'user.userid' and issueKey in IssueHistory()) or (updated >= -1w AND 'Last Updater' = 'user.userid') or (worklogComment ~ 'user.userid' and worklogDate >= '_TIMECARDSTART_' and worklogDate < '_TIMECARDEND_') or (worklogAuthor = 'user.userid' and worklogDate >= '_TIMECARDSTART_' and worklogDate < '_TIMECARDEND_')) AND ('Project - Subproject' is empty OR 'Project - Subproject' not in ('10705 - LandsEnd.com Support', '10345 - Administration', '10558 - Run the Business') OR issuetype = 'Sub-task')) ORDER BY Project, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Proj - General
issueGroups.query: project = LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND labels in (LECOM) AND (Labels NOT in (TIMETRACK) OR Labels is EMPTY)  AND ('Project - Subproject' is empty OR 'Project - Subproject' not in ('10705 - LandsEnd.com Support', '10345 - Administration', '10558 - Run the Business')) ORDER BY Project, Summary, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Al's Time Buckets for Tracking
issueGroups.query: project = LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND labels in (LECOM) AND Labels in (TIMETRACK) ORDER BY Project, Summary, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Support
issueGroups.query: ((assignee was 'user.userid' and issueKey in IssueHistory()) or (updated >= -2w AND 'Last Updater' = 'user.userid') or (worklogDate > -4w and worklogComment ~ 'user.userid')) AND (Type = 'Problem' OR 'Project - Subproject' = '10705 - LandsEnd.com Support') OR (project = LE-Internal AND 'Project - Subproject' = '10705 - LandsEnd.com Support') ORDER BY Project, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Run The Business
issueGroups.query: (Labels NOT in (TIMETRACK) OR Labels is EMPTY) AND (((assignee was 'user.userid' and issueKey in IssueHistory()) or (updated >= -2w AND 'Last Updater' = 'user.userid') or (worklogDate > -4w and worklogComment ~ 'user.userid')) AND 'Project - Subproject' = '10558 - Run the Business') OR ((Labels NOT in (TIMETRACK) OR Labels is EMPTY) AND project = LE-Internal AND 'Project - Subproject' = '10558 - Run the Business') ORDER BY Project, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Administration
issueGroups.query: project = LE-Internal AND 'Project - Subproject' = '10345 - Administration' ORDER BY Project, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Tasks - Specific
issueGroups.query: project != LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND (((assignee was 'user.userid' and issueKey in IssueHistory()) or (updated >= -1w AND 'Last Updater' = 'user.userid') or (worklogComment ~ 'user.userid' and worklogDate >= '_TIMECARDSTART_' and worklogDate < '_TIMECARDEND_') or (worklogAuthor = 'user.userid' and worklogDate >= '_TIMECARDSTART_' and worklogDate < '_TIMECARDEND_')) AND ('Project - Subproject' is empty OR 'Project - Subproject' not in ('10345 - Administration', '10558 - Run the Business') OR issuetype = 'Sub-task')) ORDER BY Project, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Projects - General
issueGroups.query: project = LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND labels in (LECOM) AND (Labels NOT in (TIMETRACK) OR Labels is EMPTY)  AND ('Project - Subproject' is empty OR 'Project - Subproject' not in ('10345 - Administration', '10558 - Run the Business')) ORDER BY Project, Summary, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey

issueGroups.name: Work Breakouts - General
issueGroups.query: project = LE-Internal AND type not in ('test') AND labels in (LECOM) AND labels in (QA) AND Labels in (TIMETRACK) ORDER BY Project, Summary, 'Project - Subproject', issueKey
